title: Maytag Top Load Washer MVWX655DW
description:
In this video we take a closer look at the Maytag MVWX655DW washing machine.  To see more details or to place an order please visit us at Abt.com:   http://www.abt.com/product/88016/Maytag-4.3-Cu.-Ft.-White-Bravos-Top-Loading-Washer-MVWX655DW.html
